{{Top|leg}}
A '''wilwog''' was a creature that was displayed at domesticated sub-sentient shows, particularly the [[Annual Mid-Rim Domesticated Sub-Sentient Show]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], a wilwog named [[Itipiniwi]] was named Best in Show. It was a popular pet for [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]] on [[Gelgelar/Legends|Gelgelar]].

